guptaartiarti1998@gmail.com.text: Artisan AI automates outbound sales workflows with its AI assistant, Ava, freeing up sales teams to focus on high-value tasks.
What are the Artisan AI offerings
Artisan AI offers an all-in-one platform with AI-powered outbound automation, lead research, and personalized email writing.
What is Ava in Artisan AI
Ava is an AI-powered BDR that automates outbound sales tasks, finding leads, researching them, and writing personalized emails.
